Goocai Mwathani wa atheru
  Rui tumite iria iriku
Rugendo rukirie guthira
Twambate ma mwiri wa Roho

CHORUS
Goocai Ngai witu goocai
Goocai Mwathani wa atheru
Mathina mathiite guthira
Twambate na mwiri wa Roho

Mwathani niatuhonokirie
Ndundu ya aremi na akararia
Marakara matanakinya
Tweherie ngarari na uremi

Ngiri na ngiri cia uhonokie
Ciikariire iti-ini cia unene
Cieteteire tume mbara-ini
Twambate na mwiri wa Roho

Roho Mutheru ni aratwira
Tuiyurwo ni gukiririria
Mwathani witu ahotanire
Na wendo na gukiririria

Tuikarage na ngoro theru
Turi wira-ini wa Mwathani
Kuri thina kana gikeno
Ritwa riake no riragocwo  
